title: Chocolate fudge traybake
ingredients: ['245g porridge oats', '310g plain flour', '1 teaspoon bicarbonate of soda', '1 teaspoon salt', '225g butter, softened', '450g dark brown soft sugar', '2 eggs', '4 teaspoons vanilla extract', '1 (397g) tin condensed sweetened milk', '250g plain chocolate, chopped', '30g butter', '1/2 teaspoon salt', '60g chopped walnuts']
